window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Murder, passion and a love that breaks all vows—for fans of Outlander!</b></p> <p>Investigating a disappearance in Eilean Donan Castle, Oxford police detective James Murray is transported through time to 1310…and trapped in a dark room. James is grateful when angelic blonde Catrìona Mackenzie hears his calls for help.</p> <p>Until the Highland lady takes him prisoner. When the laird is poisoned, they join forces to catch a killer. Catrìona is destined for the nunnery. And James needs to return to the 21st century. But he can’t leave his medieval angel unprotected.</p> <p>Their love is forbidden.</p> <p>A killer is watching.</p> <p>Can love save their lives and bind them across time?</p> <p><b>Read by the award-winning narrator, Audie finalist, and Earphones for excellence in narration winner, Shane East and Marian Hussey, Earphones Award winner and ALA Listen List recipient for outstanding audiobook narration.</b></p>"; 
